&lt;p&gt;More than most of the Guards series (or Discworld in general), &lt;a data-goodreads-type=&#34;book&#34; data-goodreads-id=&#34;63720&#34; href=&#34;https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/63720.the-fifth-elephant&#34;&gt;The Fifth Elephant&lt;/a&gt; is driven by a strong plot rather than leaning on characters and jokes. It&amp;rsquo;s actually a nice change from many of the other books, although I do like both styles.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
